parameters:
Boku (Summer vacation starts tomorrow, huh... What
should I do for a whole month? Having a lot of
homework is a bit depressing, but...)

Boku (But somehow, I have a feeling it's going to
be fun!)

Takeru: "Heh heh heh... I found something cool. I
thought I'd show it to \n[1] specially."

Boku\se[4]: "Eh, something cool? Show me, show
me!"

Boku\se[1]: "But this... it's a smartphone! You
know we're not allowed to bring these to school!"

Takeru\se[4]: "Shh! Don't shout about it! Just
wait a sec, I'm getting it out... Here, \n[1],
take a look at this."
Takeru\se[2]: "Ah, idiot! Keep it down, will you!"

Takeru\se[0]: "Yeah... awesome, right? I finally
managed to bypass the smartphone filtering
yesterday."

Boku (Incredible... There's a woman straddling a
man... I don't quite understand, but it's
somehow...)

Hiromi: "Alright, confiscated. It's bad enough
bringing mobile devices to school... and on top of
that, watching such videos."

Hiromi: "Really... If you only think about naughty
things, you won't grow up to be a good adult."

Takeru\se[2]: "Damn it, it's all because \n[1]
shouted..."

Hiromi: "I see, so this is \n[10]-kun's
smartphone. I'll keep it until your mother comes
to pick it up."

Boku\se[1] (The woman in that video... was really
naughty... That was naughty...)

And so, with my heart pounding and filled with
restless excitement... my summer vacation began
